These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
City: liverpool, hannover, edinburgh, miami
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| City   | liverpool | hannover | edinburgh | miami |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, weightlifting, climbing, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Sport   | weightlifting | rowing | lacrosse | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, indie, trance, r&b
1. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of jazz is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | trance | indie | r&b |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, mauve, aquamarine, blue
1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Color   | mauve | blood-red | blue | aquamarine |

 #################################

 
