.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-8::.
House: tower, wooden, farmhouse, gothic-revival
1. the wooden house is on the left of the tower house##1
2. the farmhouse house is on the left of the wooden house##1
3. the tower house is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
4. the wooden house is on the left or right of the tower house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |   3    |   4    |
| House   | farmhouse | wooden | tower | gothic-revival |

