1. the firefighter is on the left or right of the writer##3
2. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
3. the entrepreneur is on the left of the librarian##1
4. the librarian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Job   | writer | firefighter | entrepreneur | librarian |

