.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, august, february, july
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in july##2
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Birthday   | july | august | november | february |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-11::.
