2. the person eating artichoke is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
3. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2    |     3      |   4    |
| Food   | zucchini | radish | artichoke | lime |

