.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-12::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, swisher, game, baccarat
1. the game-smoker is between the baccarat-smoker and the swisher-smoker##2
2. the game-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |    4     |
| Cigar   | swisher | game | baccarat | pall-mall |

 #################################

 
