.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-17::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, bellflower, poppy, azalea
1. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
2. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
3. the person who growspoppy is between the person who growsbellflower and the person who growsazalea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2  |   3    |     4     |
| Flower   | azalea | poppy | bellflower | aconite |

